Simulated German HAI weekly series, 2011–2012

Source: R/data-doc.R
sim_weekly.Rd

Simulated German HAI weekly series, 2011–2012

Usage

sim_weekly

Format

A tibble with columns:

date

Date for ISO week start (Monday)

year

Integer year

iso_week

Integer ISO week number

hai

Character infection type

cases_week

Integer simulated cases

deaths_week

Integer simulated deaths

dalys_week

Numeric simulated DALYs
